Sid Smith (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sid_Smith_(actor) 0 Sidney Smith (February 28, 1894 – July 4, 1928), known on-screen as Sid Smith, was an American actor. He acted in and directed many silent films. He died of alcohol poisoning from bad liquor. Sidney_Smith ( February_28_,_1894 – July_4_,_1928 ) , known_on-screen as Sid_Smith , was an_American_actor . He acted in and directed many_silent_films . He died of alcohol_poisoning from bad_liquor .
